《英雄本色3》的線上多人遊戲中的地圖、遊戲模式、獎勵、排名以及戰隊會有動態的改變。<ref name="hashtag">{{cite web | url=http://www.digitalspy.com.au/gaming/news/a356529/max-payne-3-competition-winners-to-appear-in-game.html | title='Max Payne 3' competition winners to appear in game | publisher=Digitalspy.com | date=2012-12-18 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Langshaw, Mark | language=en | archive-date=2013-01-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130128163323/http://www.digitalspy.com.au/gaming/news/a356529/max-payne-3-competition-winners-to-appear-in-game.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

