=== 劇情 ===
根據Rockstar員工Sam Houser，他們打算在此作為主角Max Payne展開一個全新的故事，他表示：「這將會是一位我們從未見過的Max Payne，他變得更老，而且比以前變得更憤世嫉俗。」在前作中，一份新聞稿表示Max離開了[[紐約市|紐約市]]，但在新的落腳地被出賣，而他就此決定要找出真相。<ref name="rockstarwatch article">{{cite web | url=http://www.rockstarwatch.net/news/734/Max-Payne-3-Announced/ | title=Max Payne 3 Announced! | publisher=RockstarWatch.net | date=2009-03-23 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Collins, AJ | language=en | archive-date=2015-01-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150104203921/http://www.rockstarwatch.net/news/734/Max-Payne-3-Announced | dead-url=yes }}</ref>而此作的背景則設定在[[巴西|巴西]][[聖保羅_(巴西)|聖保羅]]，Max在這裡為一個當地的富裕家族Branco家族工作，時間則是前作的八年後。<ref name="pc world article">{{cite web | url=http://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/article/384483/rockstar_releases_new_max_payne_3_info | title=Rockstar releases new Max Payne 3 info | publisher=PC World Australia | date=2011-04-27 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Simpson, Campbell | language=en | archive-date=2020-11-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126020458/https://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/article/384483/rockstar_releases_new_max_payne_3_info | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.joystiq.com/2009/06/13/max-payne-3-details-from-game-informer-hit-the-web | title=Max Payne 3 details from Game Informer hit the web | publisher=Joystiq | date=2009-06-13 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Gilbert, Ben | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120529195809/http://www.joystiq.com/2009/06/13/max-payne-3-details-from-game-informer-hit-the-web/ | archive-date=2012-05-29 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>Max決定在地落地以忘記過去的一切。但在一次家族的男主人Rodrigo Branco的妻子被綁架後，Max即被捲入一宗關連著整個聖保羅市陰謀，而他身邊的所有人及所有事物都被捲進當中。

=== 角色 ===
Rockstar在初時表示，James McCaffrey將不會再延續為Max Payne配音的工作，並會由另一位較年老的配音員代替。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.joystiq.com/2009/06/15/max-payne-3-gets-different-older-voice-actor/ | title=Max Payne 3 gets different, older voice actor | publisher=Joystiq | date=2009-06-15 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Gilbert, Ben | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111220010148/http://www.joystiq.com/2009/06/15/max-payne-3-gets-different-older-voice-actor/ | archive-date=2011-12-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>但是，[[EDGE|EDGE]]雜誌則說他除了繼續配音工作之餘，亦會充當遊戲的[[動作捕捉|動作捕捉]]中Max Payne的部份。<ref name="EDGEMAY2011" />

== 遊戲開發 ==
{{quote box|align=right|width=30%|quote=我們慶幸我們有機會看到真正的遊戲畫面並且給予反饋。我們一直都有和[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar]]進行會議，當我們看到《英雄本色3》後，我們覺得它看起來很驚人——其中一件值得我們開心的事是，我們可以給開發小組關於我們對該遊戲的感覺而不用親自製作遊戲。Rockstar所推出的遊戲向來都有質素保證，基本上玩家都可確保這將會是一款優質遊戲。正如我們[[Remedy_Entertainment|Remedy]]，Rockstar品牌本身就是一個品質保證。我們很開心成為開發工作的一份子，但我們不願意曝光於媒體中。在我們眼中看到的遊戲，此作將會是非常棒的。 |source=Oskari Hakkinen<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.vg247.com/2012/01/09/quick-quotes-remedys-hakkinen-on-phenomenal-max-payne-3/ | title=Quick quotes: Remedy’s Hakkinen on “phenomenal” Max Payne 3 | publisher=VG247.com | date=2012-01-09 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Cullen, Johnny | language=en | archive-date=2020-10-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031172659/https://www.vg247.com/2012/01/09/quick-quotes-remedys-hakkinen-on-phenomenal-max-payne-3/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><br />[[Remedy_Entertainment|Remedy Entertainment]]遊戲開發部負責人}}

《英雄本色3》原來計劃於2009年的下半年推出。<ref name="rockstarwatch article" />但之後本作的推出日期被推遲到2010年連同Rockstar的母公司[[Take-Two_Interactive|Take-Two Interactive]]其他數款遊戲同時握出，而他們表示原因是「從更多的開發時間中獲得更大的利益」。2010年6月，遊戲再次被推遲至2011年。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rockstarwatch.net/news/984/Max-Payne-3-delayed-Redemption-sells-5-million-GTAIV-sells-17-million/ | title=Max Payne 3 delayed; Redemption sells 5 million; GTAIV sells 17 million | publisher=RockstarWatch.net | date=2010-06-08 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Collins,  AJ | language=en | archive-date=2017-07-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703150834/http://www.rockstarwatch.net/news/984/Max-Payne-3-delayed-Redemption-sells-5-million-GTAIV-sells-17-million/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>同年的12月21日，遊戲並沒有在Take-Two Interactive 2011年的推出日程中出現，顯示此作第四度被延期推出。<ref name="pc world article" /><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/280887/max-payne-3-skips-take-twos-2011-2012-release-schedule/ | title=Max Payne 3 skips Take-Two's 2011-2012 release schedule | publisher=ComputerAndVideoGames.com | date=2010-12-17 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Ivan, Tom | language=en | archive-date=2014-12-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224182546/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/280887/max-payne-3-skips-take-twos-2011-2012-release-schedule/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>後來[[IGN|IGN]]的一篇報導稱《英雄本色3》仍然在開發，而非被取消或暫停，同時Rockstar釋出了兩張新的遊戲截圖。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://au.pc.ign.com/articles/115/1158525p1.html | title=Proof: Max Payne 3 is Still Alive | publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] | date=2011-03-31 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Reilly, Jim | language=en}}</ref>

2011年9月8日，Rockstar公佈《英雄本色3》將會在2012年3月正式推出<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/18761/max-payne-3-coming-march-2012.html | title=Max Payne 3 Coming March 2012 | publisher=[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar Games]] | date=2011-09-08 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | language=en | archive-date=2020-11-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111234102/http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/18761/max-payne-3-coming-march-2012.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>；而數天後Rockstar公開了遊戲作品的第一段預告片。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ibtimes.com/articles/211832/20110911/max-payne-3-rockstar-ps3-xbox-360-trailer-reveal-arrival-games.htm | title=Revealed: Max Payne 3 Trailer Arriving on September 14 | publisher=International Business Week | date=2011-09-11 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | language=en | archive-date=2012-03-29 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66W5KY9ST?url=http://www.ibtimes.com/articles/211832/20110911/max-payne-3-rockstar-ps3-xbox-360-trailer-reveal-arrival-games.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2392966,00.asp | title=Rockstar Games Releases First Max Payne 3 Trailer | publisher=PCMag.com | date=2011-09-14 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Shoemaker, Natalie | language=en | archive-date=2016-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205540/http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2392966,00.asp | dead-url=no }}</ref>預告片在9月14日公開<ref>{{cite web | url=http://daxgamer.com/2011/09/max-payne-3s-debut-trailer/ | title=Max Payne 3's Debut trailer | publisher=Daxgamer | date=2011-09-14 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=John | language=en | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084840/http://daxgamer.com/2011/09/max-payne-3s-debut-trailer/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。針對於有評論批評遊戲放棄了前作的黑色電影風格，遊戲系列前作的編劇山姆·萊克表示，《英雄本色3》將保持一貫的黑暗和堅韌不拔的風格，而且玩家在此作更會發現驚喜<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/19121/remedys-sam-lake-and-matias-myllyrinne-talk-all-things-max-payne.html | title=Remedy's Sam Lake and Matias Myllyrinne Talk All Things Max Payne | publisher=[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar Games]] | date=2011-10-07 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | language=en | archive-date=2020-08-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805134058/https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/19121/remedys-sam-lake-and-matias-myllyrinne-talk-all-things-max-payne.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Remedy_Entertainment|Remedy Entertainment]]的CEO Oskari Hakkinen則說遊戲看起來「棒極了」。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-01-16-remedy-proud-of-rockstars-brilliant-max-payne-3 | title=Remedy "proud" of Rockstar's "brilliant" Max Payne 3 | publisher=Eurogamer | date=2012-01-16 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Phillips, Tom | language=en | archive-date=2021-02-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226193751/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-01-16-remedy-proud-of-rockstars-brilliant-max-payne-3 | dead-url=no }}</ref>次年1月，Take-Two再度將遊戲推出日期延後兩個月至2012年5月，表示是為了「確保《英雄本色3》會有最高的品質」。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-01-17-max-payne-3-release-date-delayed | title=Max Payne 3 release date delayed until May | publisher=Eurogamer | date=2012-01-17 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Phillips, Tom | language=en | archive-date=2020-11-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127023637/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-01-17-max-payne-3-release-date-delayed | dead-url=no }}</ref>

Rockstar在遊戲開發期間對於聖保羅市的文化、警察、武器等等進行了資料搜集，確保遊戲的真實性。資料搜集小組數次到達當地進行實地搜查，包括當地的黑勢力、警察以及特種部隊的裝備及武器選擇<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/331622/rockstar-details-research-behind-max-payne-3s-seedy-brazilian-world/ | title=Rockstar details research behind Max Payne 3's seedy Brazilian world | publisher=ComputerAndVideoGames.com | date=2012-01-10 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Denton, Jake | language=en | archive-date=2014-12-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209062107/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/331622/rockstar-details-research-behind-max-payne-3s-seedy-brazilian-world/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2011年11月Gamasutra的一次訪問中，Rockstar的Dam Houser表示，其實公司開發《英雄本色3》的想法已有一段時間，只是因為公司的資源不夠和開發小組不足而使他們相隔八年才推出續作。而且開發小組亦打算在推出《[[江湖本色2|江湖本色2]]》後用一段時間來冷靜下來，並且認真考慮他們的下一個計劃<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/6550/dan_houser_on_how_rockstar_does_it.php?page=2 | title=Dan Houser On How Rockstar Does It | publisher=Gamasutra | date=2011-11-18 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Morris, Chris | language=en | archive-date=2021-02-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224184706/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/6550/dan_houser_on_how_rockstar_does_it.php?page=2 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
== 市場情況 ==

《江湖本色3》是Rockstar Games花費最多於市場推廣的一款遊戲，遊戲除了電視廣告及戶外廣告外，亦會在[[歐洲聯賽冠軍盃|歐洲聯賽冠軍盃]]上播出廣告片段<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.vg247.com/2012/03/07/max-payne-3-to-be-rockstars-biggest-and-boldest-marketing-effort-thus-far/ | title=Max Payne 3 to be Rockstar’s “biggest and boldest marketing effort thus far” | publisher=VG247.com | date=2012-03-07 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Cullen, Johnny | language=en | archive-date=2021-02-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208191916/https://www.vg247.com/2012/03/07/max-payne-3-to-be-rockstars-biggest-and-boldest-marketing-effort-thus-far/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

Rockstar Games在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上舉行了一場比賽，用家於2012年1月13日在他們的tweet中加入「#MaxPayne3」的[[hashtag|hashtag]]就有機會被抽中在多人遊戲中加入他們的肖像<ref name="hashtag" />。Rockstar同時和多個零售商合作，預訂了遊戲的玩家將可優先獲得「Cemetery Multiplayer Map」地圖包、「The Silent Killer Multiplayer Loadout Pack」多人遊戲擴充包（包括輕型反坦克武器、可快速逃離戰火的「Slippery Character Burst」和放大敵人聲音的「Listening Device Item」）以及可以免費得到會在未來推出的付費多人遊戲DLC擴充包。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/20061/max-payne-3-preorder-exclusive-bonuses-for-europe-and-australia.html | title=Max Payne 3 Pre-Order Exclusive Bonuses for Europe and Australia | publisher=[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar Games]] | date=2012-01-16 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | language=en | archive-date=2021-01-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127140744/https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/20061/max-payne-3-preorder-exclusive-bonuses-for-europe-and-australia.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>Rockstar同時推出了《江湖本色3》的特別版（Special Edition），玩家可在2012年4月2日前預訂特別版。而在特別版中包括了一個10吋高的Max Payne收藏像、「Original Still Life」遊戲系列版畫藝術本、一個子彈形的鑰匙扣、《英雄本色3》官方原聲碟和額外的多人遊戲擴充內容（包含系列前作的角色和武器）<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-11-21-max-payne-3-special-edition-detailed | title=Max Payne 3 special edition detailed | publisher=Eurogamer | date=2011-11-21 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | author=Dutton, Fred | language=en | archive-date=2012-07-31 | archive-url=https://archive.is/20120731025629/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-11-21-max-payne-3-special-edition-detailed | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/20081/max-payne-3-special-edition-preorder-deadline-extended-to-april-.html | title=Max Payne 3 Special Edition Pre-Order Deadline Extended to April 2nd | publisher=[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar Games]] | date=2012-01-17 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | language=en | archive-date=2020-10-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029163349/https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/20081/max-payne-3-special-edition-preorder-deadline-extended-to-april-.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]和[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]版本分別會送出[[Xbox_Live|Xbox Live]] [[Avatar|Avatar]]或[[PlayStation_Home|PlayStation Home]]的獎勵<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/20131/classic-max-payne-avatar-items-now-available-on-xbox-live.html | title=Classic Max Payne Avatar Items Now Available on Xbox LIVE | publisher=[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar Games]] | date=2012-01-13 | accessdate=2012-03-10 | language=en | archive-date=2020-08-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813205236/https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/20131/classic-max-payne-avatar-items-now-available-on-xbox-live.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。而Rockstar Games亦開設了「Rockstar Games Social Club」以讓玩家查看已登記玩家的遊戲統計數據及一系列的比賽和獎勵。

